#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.40"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.40:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.40:0.2"
msgid "4. Dānavagga"
msgstr "4. Giving"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 40. Duccaritavipākasutta → apāyasaṃvattanikasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.40:0.3"
msgid "40. Duccaritavipākasutta"
msgstr "40. The Results of Misconduct"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.40:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pāṇātipāto, bhikkhave, āsevito bhāvito bahulīkato nirayasaṃvattaniko "
"tiracchānayonisaṃvattaniko pettivisayasaṃvattaniko."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, the killing of living creatures, when cultivated, developed, "
"and practiced, leads to hell, the animal realm, or the ghost realm."

#. VAR: sabbalahuso → sabbalahusoti sabbalahuko (s-a)
msgctxt "an8.40:1.2"
msgid ""
"Yo sabbalahuso pāṇātipātassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa appāyukasaṃvattaniko "
"hoti. (1)"
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is a short life span."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.40:2.1"
msgid ""
"Adinnādānaṃ, bhikkhave, āsevitaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ nirayasaṃvattanikaṃ "
"tiracchānayonisaṃvattanikaṃ pettivisayasaṃvattanikaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Stealing, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the "
"animal realm, or the ghost realm."

msgctxt "an8.40:2.2"
msgid ""
"Yo sabbalahuso adinnādānassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa "
"bhogabyasanasaṃvattaniko hoti. (2)"
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is loss of wealth."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.40:3.1"
msgid ""
"Kāmesumicchācāro, bhikkhave, āsevito bhāvito bahulīkato nirayasaṃvattaniko "
"tiracchānayonisaṃvattaniko pettivisayasaṃvattaniko."
msgstr ""
"Sexual misconduct, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, "
"the animal realm, or the ghost realm."

msgctxt "an8.40:3.2"
msgid ""
"Yo sabbalahuso kāmesumicchācārassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa "
"sapattaverasaṃvattaniko hoti. (3)"
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is rivalry and enmity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.40:4.1"
msgid ""
"Musāvādo, bhikkhave, āsevito bhāvito bahulīkato nirayasaṃvattaniko "
"tiracchānayonisaṃvattaniko pettivisayasaṃvattaniko."
msgstr ""
"Lying, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the animal "
"realm, or the ghost realm."

msgctxt "an8.40:4.2"
msgid ""
"Yo sabbalahuso musāvādassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa "
"abhūtabbhakkhānasaṃvattaniko hoti. (4)"
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is false accusations."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an8.40:5.1"
msgid ""
"Pisuṇā, bhikkhave, vācā āsevitā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nirayasaṃvattanikā "
"tiracchānayonisaṃvattanikā pettivisayasaṃvattanikā."
msgstr ""
"Divisive speech, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, "
"the animal realm, or the ghost realm."

msgctxt "an8.40:5.2"
msgid ""
"Yo sabbalahuso pisuṇāya vācāya vipāko, manussabhūtassa mittehi "
"bhedanasaṃvattaniko hoti. (5)"
msgstr ""
"The minimum result it leads to for a human being is being divided against "
"friends."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.248"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an8.40:6.1"
msgid ""
"Pharusā, bhikkhave, vācā āsevitā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nirayasaṃvattanikā "
"tiracchānayonisaṃvattanikā pettivisayasaṃvattanikā."
msgstr ""
"Harsh speech, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, the "
"animal realm, or the ghost realm."

msgctxt "an8.40:6.2"
msgid ""
"Yo sabbalahuso pharusāya vācāya vipāko, manussabhūtassa "
"amanāpasaddasaṃvattaniko hoti. (6)"
msgstr ""
"The minimum result it leads to for a human being is hearing disagreeable "
"things."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an8.40:7.1"
msgid ""
"Samphappalāpo, bhikkhave, āsevito bhāvito bahulīkato nirayasaṃvattaniko "
"tiracchānayonisaṃvattaniko pettivisayasaṃvattaniko."
msgstr ""
"Talking nonsense, when cultivated, developed, and practiced, leads to hell, "
"the animal realm, or the ghost realm."

msgctxt "an8.40:7.2"
msgid ""
"Yo sabbalahuso samphappalāpassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa "
"anādeyyavācāsaṃvattaniko hoti. (7)"
msgstr ""
"The minimum result it leads to for a human being is that no-one takes what "
"you say seriously."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an8.40:8.1"
msgid ""
"Surāmerayapānaṃ, bhikkhave, āsevitaṃ bhāvitaṃ bahulīkataṃ "
"nirayasaṃvattanikaṃ tiracchānayonisaṃvattanikaṃ pettivisayasaṃvattanikaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Taking alcoholic drinks that cause negligence, when cultivated, developed, "
"and practiced, leads to hell, the animal realm, or the ghost realm."

msgctxt "an8.40:8.2"
msgid ""
"Yo sabbalahuso surāmerayapānassa vipāko, manussabhūtassa "
"ummattakasaṃvattaniko hotī”ti. (8)"
msgstr "The minimum result it leads to for a human being is madness.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.40:8.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.40:8.4"
msgid "Dānavaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an8.40:9.1"
msgid "Dve dānāni vatthuñca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.40:9.2"
msgid "khettaṃ dānūpapattiyo;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.40:9.3"
msgid "Kiriyaṃ dve sappurisā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.40:9.4"
msgid "abhisando vipāko cāti."
msgstr ""
